<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8">{{> base-styles}}</head>
<body>
  <div class="sheet">
    {{> letterhead}}

    <div class="doc-head">
      <div class="doc-eyebrow">Private &amp; Confidential</div>
      <h1 class="doc-title">Letter of Warning</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="meta-row">
      <div>
        <span class="meta-k">Reference No.</span>
        <span class="meta-v">{{refNo}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="right">
        <span class="meta-k">Date of Issue</span>
        <span class="meta-v">{{generatedDate}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p class="salutation">Dear {{fullName}},</p>
      <p>
        This letter serves as a formal warning regarding the following matter concerning
        your conduct / performance as <strong>{{jobTitle}}</strong> in the
        <strong>{{department}}</strong> department:
      </p>

      <table class="kv">
        <tr><th>Subject of Concern</th><td>{{#if reason}}{{reason}}{{else}}As discussed with you{{/if}}</td></tr>
        {{#if effectiveDate}}<tr><th>Date of Incident</th><td>{{effectiveDate}}</td></tr>{{/if}}
      </table>

      <p>
        We expect all employees to uphold the standards and values of
        <strong>{{companyName}}</strong>. The above conduct is not in keeping with these
        expectations and must be addressed promptly.
      </p>
      <p>
        You are advised to take immediate corrective action. Please note that a failure to
        demonstrate sustained improvement may result in further disciplinary action, up to
        and including termination of employment.
      </p>
      <p>
        We are confident you will treat this matter with the seriousness it warrants and
        take the necessary steps to improve.
      </p>

      <div class="sign">
        <p style="margin:0 0 6px; font-size:10px; color:var(--muted);">For {{companyName}},</p>
        <div class="sign__space"></div>
        <div class="sign__rule"></div>
        <div class="sign__name">{{signatoryName}}</div>
        <div class="sign__title">{{signatoryTitle}}</div>
      </div>

      <div class="note">
        Acknowledgement of receipt: I confirm that I have received and understood the
        contents of this letter.<br/><br/>
        Employee signature: ____________________ &nbsp;&nbsp; Date: ____________________
      </div>
    </div>

    {{> footer}}
  </div>
</body>
</html>
